        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://firegpg.tuxfamily.org/index.php?page=home&amp;lang=en">FireGPG - use GPG easily in Firefox !</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Firefox extension to enable GPG encryption/verification in GMail.  Need to give this a shot.</p>

